  <description><![CDATA[<p>We are very pleased to introduce the Sport Hotel Hermitage and Spa Hotel, a wonderful, luxurious hotel with direct access to the wonderful Sport Wellness Mountain Spa included.  It is adjacent to the main Soldeu gondola and all the amenities of the are close on hand. The lovely lounge and bar areas excude charm and sophistication with tasteful furnishings. The service is excellent as expected in a 5 star hotel and there is a choice of restaurants with show cooking for you to enjoy. The spectacular Sport Wellness Mountain Spa divided on 5 floors in to different beauty and health areas including pools of different temperatures, saunas, a wide pool with hydrotherepy jets, saunas and direct access to two outdoor hot tubs. This is included for hotel guests and open to adults from 14 years. Flip flops and swimsuits are obligatory and 3 hour sessions can be booked at reception. A wide range of massages and beauty treatments are available (local charge).</p>]]></description>
